Following the standard method, for any given Spearman correlation r with sample size n, we calculated a t-statistic using the formula \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
